Nim bindings for WebUI

Example:

import webui/bindings

let window = newWindow() # Create a new Window
window.show("<html>Hello</html>", 0) # Show the window with html content in any browser

wait() # Wait until the window gets closed

webui: Webui

Consts

useWebuiDll = false
useWebuiStaticLib = false
WEBUI_DEF_TIMEOUT = 8
Default startup timeout in seconds 
WEBUI_DEFAULT_PATH = "."
Default root path 
WEBUI_HEADER_CALL_FUNC = 0x000000FA
Call a backend function 
WEBUI_HEADER_CLICK = 0x000000FD
Click event 
WEBUI_HEADER_CLOSE = 0x000000FB
Close window 
WEBUI_HEADER_JS = 0x000000FE
Javascript result in frontend 
WEBUI_HEADER_SIGNATURE = 0x000000FF
All packets should start with this 8bit 
WEBUI_HEADER_SWITCH = 0x000000FC
Frontend refresh 
WEBUI_MAX_ARRAY = 1024
Max num of threads, servers, windows, pointers... 
WEBUI_MAX_BUF = 1024000
1024 Kb max dynamic memory allocation 
WEBUI_MAX_PORT = 65500
Should be less than 65535 
WEBUI_MIN_PORT = 10000
Minimum socket port 
WEBUI_VERSION = "2.0.6"
Version
